      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Combat: 3 cards, pick 1. Rates 65% Common / 30% Uncommon / 5% Rare / 0%
    Special.

    Elite: 4 cards, pick 1. Rates 35% Common / 45% Uncommon / 18% Rare
    / 2% Special.

    Boss: 5 cards, pick 2. Rates 0% Common / 60% Uncommon / 35%
    Rare / 5% Special, then guarantee at least 2 Rare/Special cards.


    Purpose
    cap: Economy max 1 card per roll. Other purposes max 2 cards per roll.

    Consumables
    use real ConsumableDataSO assets when assigned. Zodiac = Edit Dice, Seal = Combat
    Aid, Rune = Utility Support.

    Whole-die color ore is an Edit Dice reward
    for Forge use; this demo creates Patina ore if missing.'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
